<script>
    function toggleDropdown(button) {
        var dropdownContent = button.parentElement.querySelector('.dropdown-content-thaotac');
        var allDropdowns = document.querySelectorAll('.dropdown-content-thaotac');
        allDropdowns.forEach(function (dropdown) {
            if (dropdown !== dropdownContent) {
                dropdown.style.display = 'none';
            }
        });
        dropdownContent.style.display = dropdownContent.style.display === 'flex' ? 'none' : 'flex';

    }
    document.addEventListener('click', function (event) {
        var dropdowns = document.getElementsByClassName('dropdown-content-thaotac');
        var buttons = document.getElementsByClassName('dropbtn-thaotac');
        var targetElement = event.target;
        var clickedInsideDropdown = false;
        for (var i = 0; i < dropdowns.length; i++) {
            if (dropdowns[i].contains(targetElement) || buttons[i].contains(targetElement)) {
                clickedInsideDropdown = true;
                break;
            }
        }
        if (!clickedInsideDropdown) {
            for (var i = 0; i < dropdowns.length; i++) {
                dropdowns[i].style.display = 'none';
            }
        }
    });

</script>
<script>

    function HuyDeHocLaiLopHocPhanDangKy(el, guid, textconfirm) {
        var idDK = $(el).data('idlhpdk');
        var msgInvalid = 'Dữ liệu kh&#244;ng hợp lệ';
        if (!idDK || !guid) {
            showPopUpMessage(msgInvalid);
            return false;
        }
        var msgConfirm = `Hủy đăng ký để học lại môn <span class='red-label'>[${$.trim(textconfirm)}]</span>, nếu bạn đồng ý thì môn học này sẽ đánh giá không đạt, bạn có đồng ý?`;
        $.confirm({
            title: '',
            icon:'fa fa-exclamation-triangle jsconfirm-icon-exclamation',
            theme: 'modern',
            type: 'red',
            animation: 'rotateX',
            backroundDismiss: false,
            scrollToPreviousElement: false,
            scrollToPreviousElementAnimate: false,
            /*boxWidth: '550px',*/
            useBootstrap: false,
            closeIcon: false,
            draggable: false,
            content: `<div><p style='font-size: 16px;color: #0E5777;font-weight: bold;text-align:justify;'>${msgConfirm}</p></div>`,
            buttons: {
                confirm: {
                    action: function () {
                        var send = {
                            param: {
                                IDDangKyHocPhan: idDK,
                                GuidIDDangKyLopHocPhan: guid
                            }
                        };
                        processHuyDeHocLai(send);
                    },
                    text: 'Đồng &#253;',
                    btnClass: 'btn-blue round-border-3',
                },
                cancel: {
                    action: function () { },
                    text: 'Đ&#243;ng',
                    btnClass: 'btn-red round-border-3',
                },
            },
        });
    }

    function processHuyDeHocLai(send) {
        $.ajax({
            url: "/SinhVienDangKy/HuyDangKyHocPhanDeHocLai",
            type: 'POST',
            data: send,
            dataType: 'json',
            success: function (e) {
                var jsonResult = e;
                if (jsonResult != null && jsonResult != undefined) {
                    if (jsonResult.Code == "00") {
                        showPopUpMessage(jsonResult.Message, 'green');
                    } else {
                        showPopUpMessage(jsonResult.Message, 'orange');
                    }
                }
            }
        });
    }

    function showPopUpMessage(message, color) {
        color = color || 'blue';
        var iconClass = "";
        switch (color) {
            case "blue":
                iconClass = "fa fa-frown-o jsconfirm-icon-fullsize";
                break;
            case "orange":
                iconClass = "fa fa-times-circle-o jsconfirm-icon-fullsize";
                break;
            case "green":
                iconClass = "fa fa-check-circle-o jsconfirm-icon-fullsize";
                break;
            default:
        }
        $.alert({
            title: '',
            icon: iconClass,
            type: color,
            theme: 'modern',
            /*boxWidth: '450px',*/
            useBootstrap: false,
            draggable: false,
            scrollToPreviousElement: false,
            scrollToPreviousElementAnimate: false,
            content: `<div style='font-size: 16px;color: #0E5777;font-weight: bold;'>${message}</div>`,
            buttons: {
                confirm: {
                    action: function () { },
                    text: 'Đ&#243;ng',
                    btnClass: `btn-${color} round-border-3`,
                }
            },
            animation: 'rotateY',
            backroundDismiss : false
        });

        //$('<div id="boxes" style="height: inherit !important;"><div id="dialog" class="window" style="height: inherit !important;position: fixed; width:350px; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); display: block;padding-bottom: 15px;"><div class="content text-center"></div><div class="text-center"><button onclick="closePopup()" class="btn btn-sm btn-save">Đóng</button></div></div><div id="mask" style="width: 100%; height: 100vh; display: block; opacity: 0.9;"></div></div>').appendTo(document.body);
        //$('#boxes .content').html('<b>' + message + '</b>');
    }
</script>

                    function loadKhaoSatDanhGiaXemDiem(idLHP) {
                        closePopup();
                        $.ajax({
                            url: "/SinhVienDiem/GetKhaoSatDanhGiaXemDiem",
                            type: 'POST',
                            data:
                            {
                                pIDLopHocPhan: idLHP
                            },
                            dataType: 'html',
                            beforeSend: function () {
                                closePopup();
                                loadingMark();
                            },
                            success: function (data) {
                                $('.k-loading-mask').remove();
                                showPopUpKhaoSat(data);
                            }
                        });
                    }
                    function showPopUpKhaoSat(content) {
                        $('<div id="boxes"><div id="dialog" class="window" style="overflow-y: scroll !important;"><a onclick="closePopup()"  class="closePopup agree"></a><div class="content"></div><div class="text-center"></div></div><div id="mask"></div></div>').appendTo(document.body);
                        $('#boxes .content').html('<p>' + content + '</p>');
                    }

                    function closePopup() {
                        $('#mask').hide();
                        $('.window').hide();
                        $('#boxes').remove();
                    }
                    function loadingMark() {
                        var html = '<div class="k-loading-mask" style="width: 100%;height: 100%;top: 0px;left: 0px;z-index: 100000;display: block;background-color: #607d8b2b;"><i class="fa fa-spinner fa-pulse fa-3x fa-fw" style="position:absolute;top:10px;left:50%;color:#397FAE;margin-top:20%;margin-left:-45px;font-size:90px;"></i></div>';
                        $(html).appendTo(document.body);

                    }
                    function showDataLHP(idLHP) {
                        var url = '/SinhVienDiem/ChiTietKetQuaHocTapMon';

                        var datas = JSON.stringify({ 'pIDLopHocPhan': idLHP });
                        $.ajax({
                            url: url,
                            type: 'Post',
                            async: false,
                            datatype: "html",
                            contentType: 'application/json; charset=utf-8',
                            data: datas,
                            success: function (data) {
                                if (data.Errors != null && data.Errors != undefined && data.Errors.Warning != undefined && data.Errors.Warning != null) {
                                    $.warning(data.Errors.Warning.errors[0]);
                                }
                                else if (data != null && data != "" && !data.includes("Errors")) {
                                    $('<div id="popup-ChiTietDiem"></div>').appendTo(document.body);
                                    $('#popup-ChiTietDiem').html(data);
                                    var popup = $('#popup-ChiTietDiem').kendoWindow({
                                        visible: true,
                                        resizable: false,
                                        //height: 650,
                                        minHeight: 400,
                                        minWidth: 300,
                                        title: "",
                                        modal: true,
                                        deactivate: function () {
                                            this.destroy();
                                        }
                                    }).data('kendoWindow');
                                    popup.center();
                                } else {
                                        $.warning("Thực hiện không thành công");
                                }
                            },
                            error: function (err) {
                                $.warning(err);
                            }
                        });
                    }

                    function freezeTable(numOfCol) {
                        if (!numOfCol || numOfCol < 1) {
                            return;
                        }
                        setTimeout(() => {
                            $('.sticky-col').removeClass('sticky-col');
                            setTimeout(() => {
                                const $table = $('#xemDiem_aaa');
                                $($table.parent()).addClass('tbl-scrollable');
                                $table.css('border-collapse', 'separate');
                                let rows = $table.find('tbody tr');
                                $(rows).each(function (index) {
                                    let $row = $(this);
                                    let prevWidth = 0;
                                    let colspan = 0;
                                    $row.find('td').each(function (i) {
                                        colspan += parseInt(($(this).attr('colspan') || '1'), 10);
                                        if (i < numOfCol) {
                                            if (colspan <= numOfCol) {
                                                $(this).addClass('sticky-col');
                                                $(this).css('left', `${prevWidth}px`);
                                                prevWidth += $(this).outerWidth();
                                                //prevWidth += $(this)[0].offsetWidth;
                                            }
                                        }
                                    })
                                });

                                let roots = $table.find('thead tr:first-child th');
                                let rootLv2 = $table.find('thead tr:nth-child(2) th');
                                let rootLv3 = $table.find('thead tr:nth-child(3) th');
                                let colspan = 0;
                                let prevWidth = 0;
                                $(roots).each(function (r) {
                                    let $root = $(this);
                                    colspan += parseInt(($(this).attr('colspan') || '1'), 10);
                                    if (r < numOfCol) {
                                        if (colspan <= numOfCol) {
                                            $(this).addClass('sticky-col');
                                            $(this).css('left', `${prevWidth}px`);
                                            prevWidth += $(this).outerWidth();
                                            //prevWidth += $(this)[0].offsetWidth;
                                        }
                                    }
                                })

                                if (rootLv2 && rootLv2.length > 0) {
                                    prevWidth = 0;
                                    colspan = 0;
                                    let flagCol = 0;
                                    $(roots).each(function (r) {
                                        let rowSpan = parseInt(($(this).attr('rowspan') || '1'), 10);
                                        colspan += parseInt(($(this).attr('colspan') || '1'), 10);
                                        if (rowSpan >= 2) {
                                            flagCol++;
                                            prevWidth += $(this).outerWidth();
                                        }
                                        else {
                                            return false;
                                        }
                                    })

                                    $(rootLv2).each(function (r) {
                                        let $root = $(this);
                                        colspan += parseInt(($(this).attr('colspan') || '1'), 10);
                                        if ((flagCol + r) < numOfCol) {
                                            if (colspan <= numOfCol) {
                                                $(this).addClass('sticky-col');
                                                $(this).css('left', `${prevWidth}px`);
                                                prevWidth += $(this).outerWidth();
                                                //prevWidth += $(this)[0].offsetWidth;
                                            }
                                        }
                                    })
                                }
                                if (rootLv3 && rootLv3.length > 0) {
                                    prevWidth = 0;
                                    colspan = 0;
                                    let flagCol = 0;
                                    $(roots).each(function (r) {
                                        let rowSpan = parseInt(($(this).attr('rowspan') || '1'), 10);
                                        colspan += parseInt(($(this).attr('colspan') || '1'), 10);
                                        if (rowSpan == 3) {
                                            flagCol++;
                                            prevWidth += $(this).outerWidth();
                                        }
                                        else {
                                            return false;
                                        }
                                    });

                                    $(rootLv2).each(function (r) {
                                        let rowSpan = parseInt(($(this).attr('rowspan') || '1'), 10);
                                        colspan += parseInt(($(this).attr('colspan') || '1'), 10);
                                        if (rowSpan >= 2) {
                                            flagCol++;
                                            prevWidth += $(this).outerWidth();
                                        }
                                        else {
                                            return false;
                                        }
                                    })

                                    $(rootLv3).each(function (r) {
                                        let $root = $(this);
                                        colspan += parseInt(($(this).attr('colspan') || '1'), 10);
                                        if ((flagCol + r) < numOfCol) {
                                            if (colspan <= numOfCol) {
                                                $(this).addClass('sticky-col');
                                                $(this).css('left', `${prevWidth}px`);
                                                prevWidth += $(this).outerWidth();
                                                //prevWidth += $(this)[0].offsetWidth;
                                            }
                                        }
                                    })
                                }
                                setTimeout(() => { recalibrateWidth($table) }, 200);
                            }, 100)
                        })
                    }

                    function recalibrateWidth($table) {
                        if (!$table) {
                            return false;
                        }
                        var flag = false;
                        var currentWidth = $(window).width();
                        var rows = $table.find('tbody tr:not(:has(.row-head))');
                        if (rows.length < 1) {
                            return false;
                        }
                        var $row = $(rows[rows.length - 1]);
                        var totalWidth = 0;
                        $row.find('td.sticky-col').each(function (i) {
                            totalWidth += $(this).outerWidth();
                            if ((totalWidth / currentWidth * 100) >= 84) {
                                flag = true;
                                return false;
                            }
                        })
                        if (flag) {
                            $('.sticky-col').removeClass('sticky-col');
                        }
                    }
